recentReportStory.title: Australia ease to five-wicket victory
recentReportStory.subTitle: Australia v Sri Lanka, VB Series, Adelaide
recentReportStory.summary: Australia showed they could survive without their resting captain as a Simon Katich half-century and crucial middle-order contributions steered them to a five-wicket victory
recentReportStory.credit: Peter English is the Australasian editor of Cricinfo
